{#
name: Metric Monitor
description: Monitor metrics and alert when thresholds are exceeded
tags: [monitoring, metrics, threshold, alert]
parameters:
  - name: skill_name
    type: str
    description: Skill display name
    required: true
  - name: skill_description
    type: str
    description: Brief description of what metrics are monitored
    required: true
  - name: metrics
    type: str
    description: Comma-separated metric names to monitor (e.g. cpu_usage, memory_usage)
    required: true
  - name: thresholds
    type: str
    description: Threshold rules (e.g. "cpu_usage>90,memory_usage>80")
    required: true
  - name: check_interval
    type: int
    description: Check interval in seconds
    default: 60
examples:
  - "Monitor CPU and memory, alert when CPU>90% or memory>80%"
#}
---
name: {{ skill_name | kebab_case }}
description: {{ skill_description }}
metadata:
  author: owlclaw
  version: "1.0"
owlclaw:
  spec_version: "1.0"
  task_type: monitoring
  constraints:
    max_daily_calls: 1440
---
# {{ skill_name }} — 使用指南

## 目标

{{ skill_description }}

## 监控指标

- 指标：{{ metrics }}
- 检查间隔：{{ check_interval }} 秒
- 阈值规则：{{ thresholds }}

## 指标逻辑

- 定时拉取指标数据
- 按阈值规则评估，超出阈值时记录告警
- 支持多指标组合判断

## 注意事项

- metrics 为逗号分隔的指标名
- thresholds 格式示例：metric_name>value 或 metric_name<value
